00:52:30,850 --> 00:52:33,180
is hundreds of millions of...

1506
00:52:33,860 --> 00:52:34,340
Yeah,

1507
00:52:34,340 --> 00:52:38,480
hundreds of millions of electron volts,

1508
00:52:38,720 --> 00:52:40,420
maybe a billion electron volts.

1509
00:52:41,300 --> 00:52:45,180
That's huge by comparison with any optical photon

1510
00:52:45,180 --> 00:52:47,340
that you would try to do an experiment with.

1511
00:52:47,540 --> 00:52:48,220
So,

1512
00:52:48,220 --> 00:52:50,460
if this were a meson,

1513
00:52:51,280 --> 00:52:52,900
you simply could not,

1514
00:52:52,900 --> 00:52:54,380
with ordinary experiments,

1515
00:52:54,700 --> 00:52:58,120
resolve the fact that it's lopsided

1516
00:52:58,120 --> 00:53:00,080
or that it's not a sphere.

1517
00:53:00,620 --> 00:53:03,960
All you would do is measure over and over again

1518
00:53:03,960 --> 00:53:06,360
the fact that on the average it's spherical,

1519
00:53:07,040 --> 00:53:08,560
that on the average,

1520
00:53:08,720 --> 00:53:12,220
the ground state wave function is spherical.

1521
00:53:12,420 --> 00:53:13,310
And you keep measuring it

1522
00:53:13,310 --> 00:53:14,200
and measuring it and measuring it,

1523
00:53:14,280 --> 00:53:15,110
and you're not going to

1524
00:53:15,110 --> 00:53:15,940
find out it's not a sphere

