00:53:15,940 --> 00:53:18,200
until you probe it with your own eyes.

1526
00:53:18,200 --> 00:53:19,760
But you can look at things which have enough energy

1527
00:53:19,760 --> 00:53:21,420
to be able to kick

1528
00:53:21,420 --> 00:53:23,080
it into a state like this.

