1537
00:53:42,220 --> 00:53:42,740
Okay.

1538
00:53:45,480 --> 00:53:46,520
Ordinary particles,

1539
00:53:46,520 --> 00:53:51,220
if they are bosons in their ground states,

1540
00:53:52,080 --> 00:53:54,220
