1552
00:54:22,680 --> 00:54:23,600
They have a spin axis.

1553
00:54:24,160 --> 00:54:26,420
You can measure their spin along an axis.

1554
00:54:26,780 --> 00:54:28,040
They're definitely not spherical.

1555
00:54:28,440 --> 00:54:30,320
They definitely have a spin axis.

1556
00:54:32,560 --> 00:54:33,240
So,

1557
00:54:33,240 --> 00:54:35,740
quite independently of any measurement

