00:55:08,580 --> 00:55:10,940
You can think of it as having a spin axis,

1572
00:55:10,940 --> 00:55:13,040
carrying charge around,

1573
00:55:13,040 --> 00:55:15,220
forming a current.

1574
00:55:15,420 --> 00:55:17,480
And that current makes it a little electromagnet.

1575
00:55:18,180 --> 00:55:18,720
Okay,

1576
00:55:18,720 --> 00:55:19,800
so it has a magnetic moment.

1577
00:55:20,500 --> 00:55:21,680
Definitely not spherical.

1578
00:55:24,540 --> 00:55:26,760
And that should be the end of the story

1579
00:55:26,760 --> 00:55:28,920
about whether an electron is a sphere or not.

