2150
01:17:32,120 --> 01:17:33,060
Probability of x.

2151
01:17:33,860 --> 01:17:34,380
Now,

2152
01:17:34,380 --> 01:17:36,340
supposing I want to work in the momentum basis,

2153
01:17:36,340 --> 01:17:40,180
the momentum basis tells me what the

2154
01:17:40,180 --> 01:17:43,420
amplitude for the momentum to have a certain value,

2155
01:17:43,420 --> 01:17:45,420
and if I square it,

2156
01:17:45,420 --> 01:17:46,140
it gives me the

2157
01:17:46,140 --> 01:17:48,200
probability to have a certain momentum.

2158
01:17:48,920 --> 01:17:51,020
So that's a thing that's called...

2159
01:17:51,020 --> 01:17:53,720
I think we probably called it psi...

