01:18:10,640 --> 01:18:16,180
that's a thing which when you square it,

2168
01:18:16,180 --> 01:18:19,820
is

2169
01:18:19,820 --> 01:18:20,420
the probability,

2170
01:18:20,420 --> 01:18:21,890
but not the probability for the

2171
01:18:21,890 --> 01:18:23,360
