01:18:23,360 --> 01:18:24,220
but

2173
01:18:24,220 --> 01:18:26,500
the probability to have momentum p.

2174
01:18:27,800 --> 01:18:29,560
This p and this p are different.

2175
01:18:30,040 --> 01:18:31,080
One is probability,

2176
01:18:31,080 --> 01:18:32,080
one is momentum.

2177
01:18:32,840 --> 01:18:33,380
Okay,

2178
01:18:33,380 --> 01:18:35,150
what's the connection between psi of

2179
01:18:35,150 --> 01:18:36,920
x and psi twiddle of p?

2180
01:18:37,180 --> 01:18:39,180
They're Fourier conjugates of each other,

2181
01:18:39,180 --> 01:18:40,880
or Fourier transforms of each other.

2182
01:18:41,420 --> 01:18:42,820
