2184
01:18:54,220 --> 01:18:58,390
Psi twiddle of p is

2185
01:18:58,390 --> 01:19:02,560
equal to the integral over x...

2186
01:19:22,259 --> 01:19:24,080
e to the minus i px.

2187
01:19:24,380 --> 01:19:26,040
That's the Fourier transform.

2188
01:19:26,740 --> 01:19:28,060
It's a function of p,

2189
01:19:28,060 --> 01:19:28,880
not x,

2190
01:19:28,880 --> 01:19:30,520
