2193
01:19:34,840 --> 01:19:36,560
If you know what psi p is,

2194
01:19:36,560 --> 01:19:39,640
then you can reconstruct what psi of x is.

2195
01:19:39,860 --> 01:19:43,980
And so psi of x is equal to

2196
01:19:43,980 --> 01:19:48,100
the integral dp over square root of 2 pi.

2197
01:19:51,140 --> 01:19:52,920
Psi twiddle of p.

2198
01:19:54,280 --> 01:19:55,280
Only difference,

2199
01:19:55,280 --> 01:19:57,240
e to the plus i px.

2200
